item.title: CVE-2024-6460|2024-08-16T06:00:02.447Z -- unknown -- grow%20by%20tradedoubler
item.description: The Grow by Tradedoubler WordPress plugin through 2.0.21 is vulnerable to Local File Inclusion via the component parameter. This makes it possible for attackers to include and execute PHP files on the server, allowing the execution of any PHP code in those files.
